Serialized Form

  • Package photos.Entities

    • Class photos.Entities.Album

      class Album extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • currentPhotoIndex
          int currentPhotoIndex
          Integer that represents the index of a specific photo in photos
          See Also:
          • Album.getCurrentPhoto()
        • name
          String name
          String that represents the given name of the album.
        • numberOfPhotos
          int numberOfPhotos
          Integer that represents the number of photos that the album contains.
        • photos
          ArrayList<Integer> photos
          Integer ArrayList that holds references to the photos that the album contains. The photos are not actually contained in each album, but rather under the user. This ArrayList stores the index in User.photoCollection of each associated photo.
          See Also:
          • User#photoCollection
        • user
          User user
          User object that represents the user that owns the album.
        • userInfoInstance
          UserInfo userInfoInstance
          UserInfo object that represents the information of all users. Needed to access the information of the user that owns the album.

    • Class photos.Entities.Photo

      class Photo extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • caption
          String caption
          String that represents the given caption of the photo.
        • date
          Date date
          Date that represents the date that the photo was "captured"
        • dateTime
          String dateTime
          String that represents the date and time that the photo was "captured" (actually the time the photo file was last modified) in format "YYYY/MM/DD HH:MM:SS".
        • name
          String name
          String that represents the given name of the photo. The name is the pathname of the corresponding photo file.
        • numAlbumsContaining
          int numAlbumsContaining
          Integer that represents the number of albums that the photo is in.
        • tags
          ArrayList<Tag> tags
          ArrayList of Tags that holds the tags associated with the photo.

    • Class photos.Entities.User

      class User extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • albums
          ArrayList<Album> albums
          ArrayList of Albums that holds the albums associated with the user.
        • currentAlbumIndex
          int currentAlbumIndex
          Integer that represents the index of the currently selected album in User.albums.
        • name
          String name
          String that represents the username of the user.
        • photoCollection
          ArrayList<Photo> photoCollection
          ArrayList of Photoss that holds the unique photos associated with the user. Album references photos from this ArrayList, so changes to a photo are reflected across all albums.
        • tagTypes
          ArrayList<String> tagTypes
          ArrayList of Strings that holds the tag types associated with the user. Used to keep track of custom-created tags for the user.
